Hi,

Please try the following code change and let us know whether the settings are saving or not.

Open ~/wp-content/plugins/wpshapere/main-settings.php on line number around 49 search for

add_action('plugins_loaded', 'SaveSettings');

and change it to

add_action('admin_menu', 'SaveSettings');

